About Strathcona County

Strathcona County is a thriving community that is the perfect place to lay down the roots for your family. With its strong petroleum and agricultural industries as well as its tight-knit and safe community—Strathcona County is the perfect place to call home. Located between Edmonton and Elk Island National Park, Strathcona County contains plenty of urban and rural space for you to build your next home.
